{"tid":1685381,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發有圖~協青有可能出賣手足!有事盡量唔好搵佢!","createTime":"2019-10-31T13:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T14:45:26.000Z","uid":32048,"like":34,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"46d73b10999f935f1ae469faf99fd69294e2d5c8","tid":1685381,"uid":32048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EKiexX7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKiexX7.jpg&h=fd8413c9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n協青社比人發現8月偷偷地收左社署錢，然後豪言收留前線青年，不過佢冇話係社署比錢，係到扮有良心幫前線，結果比人發現就出信解釋，字裏行間係讚港鐵同政府(DLLM 佢仲要話係地鐵唔係用港鐵,仲話佢員工十分優秀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，重點係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">社署比錢既服務資料要交比交比社署!!!</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信好多手足係冇車走既時候，都有坐過校車走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我明好多時<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">候冇車走時都要焗上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>，但大家要有個保護自己既心態，盡量唔好咁易信人同講野比人聽。<br />\n<br />\n你可能問點解我有信同咁清楚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我同你都係用家，都有坐過以為有良心既校巴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W1ATOys.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1ATOys.jpg&h=bf580bc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97d7efe527fa79446caccb2861a42da78ea6d5f6","tid":1685381,"uid":202309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:35:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5bc9d791fddf939b594fcf1fee73b5f9175964be","tid":1685381,"uid":53187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:36:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b54cf071cc908ab0e264553433